  "text": "The main goal of these trials was to collect uniaxial stress-strain data for calibration of the model and setup of FE simulation. Published studies on a large panel of soft biological tissues have investigated on uniaxial experiments [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] . Heterogeneous results were reported, consecutive to variable methodologies. Therefore, we decided to carry out dedicated experiments to ensure consistency within this study.",
